<h3>Problem 4: Sum of Execution Times</h3> 

  A 4-program benchmark suite has execution times as listed below for 3
  different systems.  Assume that System-A is the reference machine.
  How does the performance of system-C compare against that of system-B?
  Show this comparison for all three metrics (sum of execution times,
  sum of weighted execution times, and GM of execution times).
  Report the comparison in terms of <b> speedup. </b>

<p>

